				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Heya, I was recently on a NToV raid with my new guild and I acquired a "Fist of Lightning":<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6828" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6828</a>.
<br />

<br />
The Haste on the Fist of Lightning is 41%. 
<br />

<br />
But anyway, I am currently using the Claw of the Savage Spirit as my offhand:<a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=10461" target="_blank" class="postlink">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=10461</a>
<br />

<br />
The effect is 41% haste with a +30 to atk mod I think.
<br />

<br />
My mainhand is the Waning Light Katar.
<br />

<br />
Now, since i play on a pvp server the 10 mr an the Fist is really really usefull, and its dmg/delay is just killer. But the statts on the Epic are much better plus the awesome STA +hp on it.  
<br />

<br />
I was thinking that they are both situational weapons.. like if I find myself in a tanking position I could throw on the epic, but for general lvling and pvping purposes to use the Fist. 
<br />

<br />
So anyway, I was hopeing that I could get your opinion on the matter. Thank you. 
<br />

<br />
--Venerable Sipid<br />_________________<br />I took the road less traveled by.......NOW I'M LOST!!!!!!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
