				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am pretty much in Jarret's camp on this one.  The FoL is nice, but it nets you 0 HP... no STA, no HP, you lose 30 atk.  As a daily driver I would have trouble giving up the epic for that fist.  15/18 is nothing to sneeze at, but I just have trouble givin up the goods.  Hell, I had a tough time convincing myself to stick <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=17385" target="_blank" class="postlink">The Rotting Fist</a> in my offhand when that came along... luckily I lost minimal HP in the process, gained a bit of AC, and it had pretty comparable (if not better) stats... I did hate to lose a 40% haste item and the 30 atk, but I hope to get a decent 41% haste before long and atk will be coming along on the eplanes gear soon, I am just taking the better dps to help on raids and hoping to get stuff to make up for that loss before long.
<br />

<br />
That being said, everyone gets to have an opinion, and I can't say its a bad weapon, just hard for me personally to give up the epic for it.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=224581" target="_blank">Venerable Yiktiki Tumbo</a>
