			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">its ratio is 41% better though, and offhand is about 40% of your non-pet DPS.  so FoL over epic is like a 16% increase in your DPS, and i don't think that stats are going to be able to give you enough of a boost to make up for anything but a small part of that gap.  if i were in an AE situation where i expected my HP/resists to matter a lot more, or if i were tanking than obviously those stats are more meaningful.  but if you're not, than the big point to stats is really just to increase your DPS and throwing away a lot of DPS from ratio for a little from stats is a bad trade.<br />_________________<br /><b><font face="tahoma"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=258749&resize=true" target="_blank">Brazzo</a>, L63 Cleric<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=664664&resize=true" target="_blank">Rhaasz Oh</a>, L56 Beastlord</font><br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=144397&resize=true" target="_blank">Hexxal</a>, L53 Shadow Knight<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23987&resize=true">Grazzo GrubGrabber</a>, L46 Druid</b></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
